title: 20. How to Be A Standout Creator on Youtube, Instagram, Podcasts + Beyond. Cultivate an Engaged Audience in Saturated 2020.
description:
Hey everyone! In today's episode you're getting me, Tess in a solo ep! I'm reflecting on my Youtube journey, starting a podcast and Instagram page + highlighting my strategies + tactics for creating a genuine + engaged audience. I hope you enjoy these tips and have the courage to step into your light + passion in 2020 and do the thing you've been wanting to do.

 Xo, Tess and Lo

Tess' Instagram @myestytessa.dermaplus + Tess' YouTube: Tess Zolly

Lauren's Instagram: @laurens.esthetics

Music by LiQwYd
